<msbt attribsize="8">
	<message label="002" attrib="01 00 00 01 00 00 00 09"><anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其實我以前<delay8 />也是做過不少傻事呢！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />比方說<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="001" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="001_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />當我還在二手商店打工的時候，<delay20 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />曾經不小心<delay8 />摔破了要賣的花瓶呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我絞盡腦汁想蒙混過去，<delay8 />於是就用黏土<delay8 />
做了個長得像花瓶的東西，<delay20 />
<anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />把它放在<delay8 />原本的地方。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />結果店裡<delay8 />來了個有錢客人，<delay20 />
<anim id="Pardon" target="actor" targetSpec="" />說什麼那花瓶充滿藝術氣息，<delay20 />
就出高價買下來啦！<pageBreak /><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我當時<delay8 />真的是拼命忍笑呢！<10_4 />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過，<delay8 />之後店長馬上發現了這件事，<delay20 />
我就被狠狠地訓一頓啦<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />很久以前，<delay20 />我有個死黨很憧憬音樂人，<delay8 />
就開始玩起了街頭演唱，<delay20 />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過對方跟我抱怨說，都沒人要停下來聽啊！<delay8 />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以呢，<delay8 />我就帶著一半看熱鬧的心情去加油，<delay20 />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />結果才發現，<delay8 />那傢伙真是個超級音痴呢！<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />於是我受不了，<delay8 />就搶走麥克風開始唱，<delay20 />
結果我反倒唱起勁來了！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Cheering" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><delay20 />還用全力大吼，<delay frames="40" /><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />於是就被痛罵一頓啦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="001_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我曾經想說，<delay8 />
一生一定要試一次吃甜食吃到吐，<delay20 />
所以就<delay8 />狂買了甜食喔！<pageBreak /><anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過，<delay20 />就在我大概吃到一半的時候，<delay8 />
就開始覺得噁心<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><size value="75" />那時我真的差點要吐了。<size value="100" /><pageBreak /><anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />也就是說人生啊，<delay20 />果然不能只有甘甜，<delay20 />
也需要有辛酸點綴才行吧？<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />說笑的啦！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="010" attrib="0b 00 00 01 00 00 00 09"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我在做家事的時候，<delay8 />
有時會犯下一些奇怪的失誤啊～<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />比方說<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="011" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="011_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />之前<delay8 />我趁著好天氣的日子<delay8 />
用洗衣機洗了衣服。<pageBreak /><anim id="Surprised" target="actor" targetSpec="" />結果我不但倒進太多洗衣精，<delay8 />
還忘了蓋洗衣機的蓋子，<delay20 />
<anim id="Oops" target="actor" targetSpec="" />泡泡就<delay8 />一團團湧了出來！<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />後來整個房間都充滿泡泡，
讓我忍不住笑了出來，<delay20 />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過最後<delay8 />我花了一整天清理呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="011_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />前陣子我努力做了料理，<delay20 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />結果試吃一口，<delay8 />才發現超級甜的！<pageBreak /><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看來我應該是把砂糖跟鹽搞錯了……<delay20 />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />竟然犯這種經典失誤，<delay8 />厲害到我自己都笑啦。<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />既然都要失敗，<delay20 />就該失敗得誇張一點，
像是誤把巧克力<delay8 />當成咖哩塊拿去煮，<delay20 />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這樣才可能生出新的料理點子啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="011_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />像我前陣子<delay20 />還想說心情不錯，<delay8 />
就用抹布來拖地好了，<delay20 />
<anim id="SadSpiral" target="actor" targetSpec="" />結果就突然<delay8 />踢飛水桶啦！<pageBreak /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我不但被彈起來的水桶打到頭，<delay8 />
房間又都是水，<delay20 />
真是超慘的啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="020" attrib="15 00 00 01 00 00 00 09"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我從小<delay20 />就有個壞毛病，<delay8 />
常會不小心就買下奇怪的東西啊。</message>
	<message label="021" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="021_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />比方說，<delay20 />家鄉的祭典上會賣的<delay8 />
草履蟲模型<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我嘴上一邊說什麼<delay20 />「誰會想買這種玩意啊」，<delay20 />
<anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />結果自己卻被祭典的氣氛沖昏頭，<delay8 />
不小心買下來了。<pageBreak /><anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />唉～<delay20 />現在想想，我當時的行為真的很莫名……<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />而且它又莫名的耐放，<delay20 />到現在還在我的老家，
簡直就是莫名其妙的化身啊，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="021_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />比方說，<delay20 />在旅途中的土產店買的<delay8 />
寫了自己名字的燈籠<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Restless" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然它放在店裡看起來很帥，<delay20 />
不過拿來裝飾房間<delay8 />卻很不搭呢，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />結果<delay8 />我就把它收著不管了。<pageBreak /><anim id="IdeaBulb" target="actor" targetSpec="" />啊，<delay8 />不過<delay frames="40" /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />之前停電的時候，<delay8 />
我剛好拿它來照明喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="021_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />比方說，<delay20 />在我老家附近會賣的<delay8 />
奇怪的土偶抱枕<tag a="110" b="0" /><pageBreak /><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />明明是個土偶，卻很柔軟，<delay8 />
我被這個矛盾的概念吸引，<delay20 />
一回過神來，<delay8 />就發現自己已經拿它去結帳啦。<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我回家之後，想說立刻用看看，<delay20 />
感受一下<delay8 />被懷古浪漫包圍的感覺<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="40" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />才怪，<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />結果它凹凸不平，<delay8 />我根本無法放鬆啊，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="030" attrib="1f 00 00 01 00 00 00 09"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />你有什麼<delay8 />喜歡的座右銘嗎？<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我有很多喔！</message>
	<message label="031" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="031_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />像是……<delay8 />「難過時<delay20 />就越要笑」！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Greeting" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這是我奶奶告訴我的。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />難過時還要露出笑容<delay8 />雖然很困難，<delay20 />
但只要實際試試，<delay20 />
就能很快重振精神，很神奇喔！<pageBreak /><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />要是你也<delay20 />碰上了難過的事，
不妨回想起這句話吧！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="031_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />「只要肯試就能成功！」<delay20 />這句話<delay20 />
真的帶給我不少勇氣啊～<pageBreak /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />別看我這樣，<delay8 />其實我以前對自己沒什麼自信，<delay20 />
常常在開始做什麼事之前<delay8 />
就先放棄了。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過<delay8 />自從有人對我說了這句話後，<delay20 />
我就開始漸漸會去挑戰，<delay20 />
<anim id="Assent" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不會在嘗試前就先否定自己囉！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="031_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Love" target="actor" targetSpec="" />「失敗為成功之母」<delay20 />這句話……<delay20 />
可是名言中的名言呢！<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所謂成功的方法，<delay20 />
就是要不斷地失敗<delay8 />才有辦法體會！<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />這句話教會我這個道理！<pageBreak /><anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />多虧這樣，<delay20 />才讓我不會
一遇到失敗就變得沮喪啊！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="040" attrib="00 00 00 01 00 00 00 09"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="040_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其實我啊，<delay8 />很喜歡聽<delay8 />
老爺爺或是老奶奶<delay8 />講以前的事喔！<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />像是以前放學後都會玩些什麼，<delay20 />
或是過去沒有電車的時候，<delay8 />
都怎麼去隔壁鎮<delay8 />之類的。<pageBreak /><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />爺爺奶奶們小時候的生活……<delay8 />
跟現在真的截然不同呢！<delay20 />
<anim id="HappyFlower" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有一堆我不知道的事，讓人好興奮喔！<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="040_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我小時候，<delay8 />曾經試著<delay8 />
讓一位腳不方便的爺爺<delay20 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />坐到貨車上，<delay8 />想送他去超市呢。<pageBreak /><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然我在出發的前一刻<delay8 />就被大人阻止了，<delay20 />
<anim id="Hesitate" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過<delay8 />爺爺還面帶微笑<delay8 />
跟我說謝謝喔！<pageBreak /><anim id="Nodding" target="actor" targetSpec="" />現在回想起來，<delay20 />
那時我是想要體貼爺爺的，<delay20 />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />結果反倒感受到了爺爺的體貼呢～<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="040_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />話說<delay8 />在我小時候，<delay20 />
有一位老婆婆每天都會<delay8 />
靜靜地坐在公園的同一張長椅上喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="Serious" target="actor" targetSpec="" />有一天，<delay8 />我鼓起勇氣向她搭話，<delay20 />
結果沒想到她超級健談，<delay20 />
<anim id="ColdChill" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我就一直聽她說話，<delay8 />聽到太陽都下山了。<pageBreak /><anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />多虧這樣，<delay8 />我就變成了一個
對假牙異常熟悉的小孩啦<tag a="110" b="0" /><tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="050" attrib="33 00 00 01 00 00 00 09"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />說起來，<delay8 />我有個喜歡<tag a="135" b="6" arg="0xcd00" />的後輩喔！<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="BigSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不知道那傢伙最近過得如何～</message>
	<message label="051" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="051_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />在搬家的時候，我給了那傢伙一本<delay8 />
《<tag a="135" b="0" arg="0xcd00" />》，<delay20 />
那傢伙好像在信中寫說<delay8 />已經讀過100遍了。
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />其實那本書，<delay20 /><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我只讀過
開頭的前三頁而已呢，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="051_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">以前去夜晚的學校試膽時，<delay20 />
<anim id="Cheering" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我大喊一聲<delay frames="12" />「哇——！」<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />來嚇那傢伙，<delay20 />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />結果那傢伙<delay8 />似乎嚇得不輕哩。<pageBreak /><anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />聽說在那之後，<delay20 />那傢伙好像有段時間
不敢晚上一個人去上廁所<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay frames="30" />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我是不是做了一件壞事啊，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="051_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />那傢伙每次吃我做的新料理時，<delay20 />
都會說著好吃，<delay8 />然後把料理全部吃完。<pageBreak /><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過<delay20 />那傢伙的體質似乎很容易吃壞肚子，<delay20 />
<anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />所以經常跑廁所喔。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不知道那傢伙現在身體有沒有好一點，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="060" attrib="3d 00 00 01 00 00 00 09"><anim id="Smiling" target="actor" targetSpec="" />最近想改變一下房間的擺設，
結果整理出<delay20 />令人懷念的相片。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Thinking" target="actor" targetSpec="" />看著照片我就回想起了往事<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="061" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="061_01" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我還年輕氣盛的時候，<delay8 />
很流行長到能拖到地面的
超級長裙喔，<tag a="110" b="6" />。<pageBreak /><anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />當時雖然也有穿迷你裙的傢伙在，<delay8 />
<anim id="SmugFace" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但我就是喜歡穿長裙。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />真虧當時的我<delay8 />能穿成那樣正常走路啊。</message>
	<message label="061_02" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00">我還年輕氣盛的時候，<delay8 />
<anim id="Grin" target="actor" targetSpec="" />學校的書包是越薄越有型喔。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="FaintSmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我會用重物壓扁，<delay8 />或是把多餘的部分縫起來……<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然書包會沒辦法裝東西挺不方便的，<delay8 />
但是那時候就是對這種事拚盡全力呢。<delay frames="40" />
<anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />某種意義上來說，我還挺率直的，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
	<message label="061_03" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我還年輕氣盛的時候，<delay8 />
濃到不行的超厚彩妝
就是有型的證明喔。<pageBreak /><anim id="AbsentMindedness" target="actor" targetSpec="" />紫色眼影加上鮮紅的口紅之類的<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="EmotEnd" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然我現在已經變得圓滑許多，<delay20 /><anim id="Laughing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />但我那
堅毅的性格當時可是表現在妝容上喔。</message>
	<message label="070" attrib="47 00 00 01 00 00 00 09">事到如今我才覺得，<delay20 />
<anim id="OhGeez" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我完全沒能<delay8 />對父母盡到孝道啊<tag a="110" b="0" /></message>
	<message label="071" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><tag a="60" b="20" /></message>
	<message label="071_01" attrib="48 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我年輕時<delay20 />還對父母擺出傲慢的態度，<delay20 />
大吼一些不該說的話。<delay frames="30" />
<anim id="Sighing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />現在想想，<delay8 />真的是很不孝呢。</message>
	<message label="071_02" attrib="48 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Negative" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我年輕時<delay20 />對父母說的話<delay8 />常感到不耐煩，<delay20 />
<anim id="WrySmile" target="actor" targetSpec="" />並因此無視他們，<delay8 />然後被無視的父母就會
大發雷霆地訓斥我說「你的回答呢？」。</message>
	<message label="071_03" attrib="48 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Explain" target="actor" targetSpec="" />我年輕時<delay8 />常做出毫無意義的叛逆行為，<delay20 />
每次跟父母吵架後都會離家出走咧。<delay40 />
<anim id="Blushing" target="actor" targetSpec="" />不過當我肚子餓時，<delay20 />就會馬上回家了。</message>
	<message label="072" attrib="00 00 00 00 00 00 00 00"><anim id="Worried" target="actor" targetSpec="" />雖然為時已晚，但我也有好好反省<tag a="110" b="0" /><delay20 />
<anim id="ShyBoy" target="actor" targetSpec="" />今後我也該<delay20 />對父母盡盡孝道了，<tag a="110" b="6" />。</message>
</msbt>